<i>adjective</i>: 성하다 [성ː하다] <i>noun</i>: 번영 [버녕], 번성 [번성], 개화 [개화] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt>성하다 [성ː하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. lively; flourishing</dd><br>
<dd>기운이나 세력이 한창 왕성하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Energy or force being strong.</dd><br>
<dd>2. thick; dense</dd><br>
<dd>나무나 풀이 싱싱하게 우거져 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>Trees or grass having grown thick and green.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>번영 [버녕]</dt><br>
<dd>prosperity; flourishing</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 사회나 조직이 번성하여 물질적으로 넉넉해짐.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of a society or organization flourishing and having material affluence.</dd><br>
<dt>번성 [번성]</dt><br>
<dd>1. prosperity; thriving</dd><br>
<dd>세력이 커져서 널리 퍼짐.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which one's force grows and prevails.</dd><br>
<dd>2. flourishing; luxuriance</dd><br>
<dd>나무나 풀이 자라서 우거져 있음.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which trees and plants grow profusely.</dd><br>
<dt>개화 [개화]</dt><br>
<dd>1. flowering; blooming</dd><br>
<dd>풀이나 나무의 꽃이 핌.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which the flowers of a plant or tree bloom.</dd><br>
<dd>2. flowering; flourishing</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 문화나 예술 등이 한창 번영함.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) A state in which culture, art, ideas, etc., thrive.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>